quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Ke kaloku izithunywa ezo zisakufika kusapho lukaLût
  15,62,"Wathi yena: “Inene ningabantu endingabaziyo mna.”"
  15,63,"Zathi zona: “Yeha! Size kuwe ngeso sohlwayo bebesoloko besithandabuza"
  15,64,Kananjalo sikuzisele inyaniso yaye sithetha inyaniso
  15,65,"Ke wena hamba ngenxalenye yobusuku nosapho lwakho, uze wena uhambe ngemva kwalo, maze kungabikho namnye kuni unyeka ngemva koko hambani niye apho niyalelwe ukuba niye khona.”"
  15,66,Ke kaloku Thina Sawenza wazeka kuye lo mmiselo wokuba iingcambu zabo bangaboni ziza kuncothulwa ekuseni ngonyezi (kusemyama)
  15,67,"Abemi besixeko (iSodom neGomora) beza bevuya (besakuva ukuba kukho amadodana amahle afikileyo kwaLût, phofu benenjongo ezikukungcola ngawo)"
  15,68,"ULût wathi: “Inene ezi ziindwendwe zam. Musani ukundihlaza kuzo"
  15,69,Kananjalo yoyikani uAllâh.”
  15,70,"Bathi bona: “Asizanga sikwalele na ukuba wena ungonwabisi okanye ukhusele nabani na endalweni?”"
  15,71,"ULût wathi: “Izizo ezi iintombi zam nje (eninokuzitshata), ukuba kunyanzelekile nenze le nto (nifuna ukuyenza)?”"
  15,72,"Inene Ndifunga6 ngobomi bakho (Muhammad) ekunxileni kwabo bubundlobongela babo, babefathula ngobumfama"
  15,73,Kanye njengoko (abakwaSâlih) bafunyanwa (sisohlwayo) ukuphuma kwelanga
  15,74,Sayiphethula (iSodom) yajonga ezantsi Sathulula imvula yamatye odongwe olutshisiweyo phezu kwabo
  15,75,Inene! Kulo eli (bali) kukho imiqondiso kwabo babonayo
  15,76,"Kananjalo izixeko ezo zazimi kuhola wendlela (ophakathi kweMakkah neSiriya, ndawo leyo namhlanje yaziwa ngokuba yiDead Sea)"
  15,77,"Inene, kwesi sehlo kukho umqondiso kwabakholwayo"
  15,78,Ke kaloku nabemi basezinkunini7 babekwangabagabadeli
  15,79,"Thina ke Sathabatha impindezelo kubo. Bona (nabaseSodom) ababesendleleni enguhola ukuba babonwe, (bacace) gca"